{"tid":2086612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會選舉防止被DQ策略","createTime":"2020-06-30T10:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T11:30:30.000Z","uid":242781,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"10e75d20539184dffaf4dce4f5e09aae19e16704","tid":2086612,"uid":242781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:44:28.000Z","msg":"國安法急住納入基本法，就係為左DQ所有曾經發表過反對國安法言論既立法會候選人。所以，而家大家見到枱面上所有泛黃嘅立法會候選人，<span style=\"color: red;\">估計基本上最後都冇可能入到閘</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，宜家好多人會質疑議會路線，但如果唔係要即刻放棄抗爭坐等共產黨滅亡，就要諗下點樣無所不用其極咁挖掘抗爭嘅資源。<br />\n<br />\n議會路線就係其中一種。選到最少自己有份糧，可以請手足做議員助理，有民意代表呢個身份去發表言論都會有多啲本地同外國媒體採納。<br />\n<br />\n但係，點樣防止被DQ？諗黎諗去都係得呢個方法：<span style=\"color: red;\">戲謔</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先睇下台灣YouTuber志褀整理世界上既戲謔政黨：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gkTw61C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgkTw61C.png&h=3bd83931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以睇晒條片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zcWqvX-kLjw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzcWqvX-kLjw&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=94e8bb49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zcWqvX-kLjw</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單啲來講，就係要<span style=\"color: red;\">未發表過反對國安法嘅政治素人</span>出嚟搞無厘頭嘅政黨。學志褀所屬政黨「歡樂無法黨」呢個名既公式，例如可以有「大麻無法黨」，唯一嘅政綱就係推動大麻合法化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者「真正共產黨」，弘揚正統共產主義思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人問，點樣確認佢係手足？嗰個候選人只要公開承諾，因為創黨嘅唯一政綱係大麻合法化，所以喺立法會裡面<span style=\"color: red;\">同大麻合法化無關嘅議案</span>全部都會投<span style=\"color: red;\">棄權</span>。當佢咁講就姐係支持攬炒，同你選個泛民入去冇分別。當然佢都可以反口，不過泛民都成日反口，都係得個信字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪睇下佢會唔會玩到咁大喺全香港人面前公開扮黃，下半世都受人身安全威脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國安法之下，<span style=\"color: red;\">戲謔</span>呢樣野其實好值得大家多啲應用。發表言論，遊行示威，甚至抗爭日常既一切行動，只要兜個彎就冇人奈得你何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb1522065f999641aa34c6a98e0460ccfda7ae2","tid":2086612,"uid":242781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:45:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15c494ee0e9bd788905d380011cebd896ee9a227","tid":2086612,"uid":242781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:46:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87f6188b1db8e66241f99d39fef58490ea90f6e7","tid":2086612,"uid":242781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:46:35.000Z","msg":"推到每區都有三四個無厘頭政黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a438351ce549a65bf7def408271ccbccd37efb","tid":2086612,"uid":242781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:47:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e7f753f5f3e87983f6407398cb1692eb1659f37","tid":2086612,"uid":242781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:48:47.000Z","msg":"大家參考多啲其他地方玩政治既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76106f04768e4f08687380627079f83d354f110d","tid":2086612,"uid":242781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:50:16.000Z","msg":"同意既麻煩幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c64ac7069d3c1adb3c882715a4782be42e0029","tid":2086612,"uid":242781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:51:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bc717767c5798d01d28aa8da70335f4258a367d","tid":2086612,"uid":242781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:54:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61f4d8798a7005c8a066d6d1dab27e682ca03adf","tid":2086612,"uid":242781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:55:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2348f4b134017bf7885d769493e8b311e2f00481","tid":2086612,"uid":242781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:59:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"147c23243cd78ac7c7e8c886936bc132d133f7bd","tid":2086612,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:30:30.000Z","msg":"好似有得做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}